# Hash-stability: every file checked out byte-for-byte identical to what was
# committed, regardless of platform. Critical because module.sig pins SHA-256
# hashes of every shipped file — a Windows checkout converting LF→CRLF would
# silently invalidate the signature.
* -text

# Re-tag the obvious binaries so git's "is this text?" diff fallback doesn't
# try to render them as text in pull requests.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.tar binary
*.tar.gz binary
*.zip binary
*.phar binary
